{"tid":1673051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"中國小粉紅襲擊加泰居民","createTime":"2019-10-24T12:25:50.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-24T13:03:50.000Z","uid":92188,"like":7,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"6df78cc1b4d113aff038def8ef977a50a3706e00","tid":1673051,"uid":92188,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T12:25:50.000Z","msg":"（推上國際！！中國人在加泰隆尼亞襲擊當地市民！）<br />\n<br />\n狠人剛剛睇立場新聞直播，見到有一班中國人在加泰隆尼亞聚集，手持中國國旗及唱國歌。立場記者上前問點解佢哋係到，佢哋表示知道今日有集會支持香港，佢哋要喺到表示無人可以分裂國家；之後鏡願影到幾個中國人圍住一名加泰隆尼亞女士，一名中國男子起踢跌向一名加泰隆尼亞女士，並搶去她手持的標語（上面寫了中文：「光復香港、時代革命￼￼」）￼及再將標語撕成碎片，行為令人髮指！！<br />\n<br />\n記者訪問該名女子，￼知道她是土生土長的加泰隆尼亞居民，今日是來支持香港人追求民主自由！￼￼￼<br />\n<br />\n立場直播（34分鐘開始睇）：<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2174835412617476/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Fstandnewshk%2Fvideos%2F2174835412617476%2F&d=wRNUG5%2F8jzvhtT%2FDMFjpNv5uq9964iqXyfozsjiZLe8%3D&h=7363c2b6\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/standnewshk/videos/2174835412617476/</a><br />\n<br />\n華爾街狼人"},{"pid":"6efc1d30e22aed7930b47e8fa75a93eb90450f13","tid":1673051,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T12:29:34.000Z","msg":"Push"},{"pid":"eaba00e7dad1804759523d6b0ec8ed6d2642bad7","tid":1673051,"uid":165683,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T12:29:48.000Z","msg":"煲大佢"},{"pid":"5a214dec9fe8838df0a04f8404d4e5142c928706","tid":1673051,"uid":169195,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T12:30:33.000Z","msg":"好複雜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7adf78255a630bc7bf4e08d291372d8702551780","tid":1673051,"uid":76776,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T12:31:11.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"a1e6e7a14ffd14143dd0a033fd884cea04f2a58e","tid":1673051,"uid":57309,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-24T12:31:14.000Z","msg":"屌啊"},{"pid":"8106c45b6e4bd